data.description: Welcome to the lovely home of 1253 Eleanor Avenue, centrally located between West Sylvania and West Laskey. This 2 story home features a spacious living room, 3 bedrooms and a dining room with plenty of room for 6 or more. The roof was replaced approximately in 2013. The hot water tank is newly installed as of 2021 and the furnace in 2018. The fenced in yard space is big enough to enjoy the outdoors, yet wont tie up all day Saturday mowing!
